snippet.title: Arbiter - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
A first look at early gameplay in the upcoming Arbiter, an action-adventure game focused on transformation in combat. The Arbiter has the unique ability to transform between light and dark powers, allowing him to fight back against demonic spirits. 

Arbiter is being developed for Windows PC.
